<h2>Manuscript Submission</h2>

<p>If you are unsure whether your paper is suitable for <em>PLOS Genetics</em>, you can send a <a href="${guidelinesURL}#presubs" title="Send a Presubmission Inquiry to PLOS Genetics">Presubmission Inquiry</a>.</p>

